explicitInput.esqlQuery:
TS metrics-collectortelemetry.otel-* | STATS BY service.instance.id, service.name 
| EVAL identifier = CONCAT(service.instance.id, " (",service.name,")")
| KEEP identifier
explicitInput.title: instance

explicitInput.esqlQuery:
FROM metrics*
| WHERE otelcol_receiver_accepted_spans IS NOT NULL
| STATS transport = VALUES(transport) BY service.instance.id
| GROK ?instance """(?<target_instance>[^(]*) \(.*\)"""
| WHERE target_instance == service.instance.id
| EVAL transport = MV_APPEND(transport, "--ALL--")
| MV_EXPAND transport
| STATS BY transport
| SORT transport
explicitInput.title: traces_receiver_transport

explicitInput.esqlQuery:
FROM metrics*
| WHERE otelcol_processor_incoming_items IS NOT NULL
| WHERE otel.signal == "traces"
| STATS processor = VALUES(processor) BY service.instance.id
| GROK ?instance """(?<target_instance>[^(]*) \(.*\)"""
| WHERE target_instance == service.instance.id
| EVAL processor = MV_APPEND(processor, "--ALL--")
| MV_EXPAND processor
| STATS BY processor
| SORT processor

query.esql:
TS metrics*
| WHERE ?trace_receiver == "--ALL--" OR (receiver IS NOT NULL AND ?trace_receiver == receiver)
| WHERE ?traces_receiver_transport == "--ALL--" OR (transport IS NOT NULL AND ?traces_receiver_transport == transport)
| KEEP @timestamp, otelcol_receiver_accepted_spans, receiver, transport, service.instance.id
| STATS spans_rate = SUM(RATE(otelcol_receiver_accepted_spans)) BY Time = BUCKET(@timestamp, 100, ?_tstart, ?_tend), service.instance.id
| GROK ?instance """(?<target_instance>[^(]*) \(.*\)"""
| WHERE target_instance == service.instance.id

query.esql:
TS metrics*
| WHERE data_type == "traces"
| WHERE ?trace_exporter == "--ALL--" OR (receiver IS NOT NULL AND ?trace_exporter == exporter)
| KEEP @timestamp, metrics.otelcol_exporter_queue_capacity, metrics.otelcol_exporter_queue_size, exporter, service.instance.id
| STATS capacity = SUM(LAST_OVER_TIME(metrics.otelcol_exporter_queue_capacity)),
    queue_size = SUM(LAST_OVER_TIME(metrics.otelcol_exporter_queue_size)) 
  BY Time = BUCKET(@timestamp, 100, ?_tstart, ?_tend), service.instance.id
| GROK ?instance """(?<target_instance>[^(]*) \(.*\)"""
| WHERE target_instance == service.instance.id
| EVAL queue_utilization = queue_size::double / capacity::double
| KEEP Time, queue_utilization
